,"department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":109196,"known_for_department":"Writing","name":"Kazuki Nakashima","original_name":"中島かずき","popularity":1.8326,"profile_path":"/1j5hgm1Gd8vEksG0yCTCDKx6A4w.jpg","credit_id":"6741eea4aab722bfa7c8edf6","department":"Writing","job":"Screenplay"}],"id":96942}},"person_1510022_translations":{"at":1774731923791,"data":{"id":1510022,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Gong Seung-Yeon, born Yoo Seung-Yeon, is a South Korean actress. She initially trained as a singer for seven years under the company SM Entertainment but left after losing interest in singing. She made her tv debut in 2012 with I Love Lee Tae-Ri. She has also worked in music videos, show hosting, and as an honorary ambassador in 2014 for the Korean National Tuberculosis Association and in 2016 for the 8th DMZ International Documentary Film Festival. She's the older sister of Yoo Jeong-Yeon, a member of the girl group Twice.","name":"Gong Seung-yeon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"Гун Син-Йон - південнокорейська акторка та модель.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"공승연","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"Gong Seung Yeon, rodným jménem Yoo Seung Yeon, je jihokorejská herečka. Je starší sestrou zpěvačky Yoo Jeong Yeon ze skupiny TWICE. Poprvé se vypracovala na zpěvačku pod společností SM Entertainment poté, co v roce 2005 vyhrála část soutěže \"Best Looks\" v soutěži SM Teen Best. V roce 2012 oficiálně debutovala jako modelka pro reklamu \"White\" společnosti Yuhan-Kimberly. Poté debutovala jako herečka v seriálu \"I Love Italy\". V roce 2015 na sebe jako relativní nováček upozornila, když se zapojila do čtvrté série korejské reality show We Got Married, kde tvořila pár se zpěvákem a hercem Lee Jong Hyunem.\n\nZískala několik ocenění. Stala se čestnou velvyslankyní \"Korejské národní asociace pro tuberkulózu\" (2014) a \"8. mezinárodního festivalu dokumentárních filmů DMZ\" (2016).  V roce 2018 také nazpívala OST k filmu \"My Dream Class\", Like a Star (s Yoo Jeong-yeon). Podílela se také na muzikálech a divadelních dílech: \"Porgy a Bess jako Clara\" (2011), respektive \"Král Lear jako princezna Goneril\" (2011).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"孔升妍（朝鲜语：공승연 Gong Seung Yeon，1993年2月27日－），本名俞昇延（朝鲜语：유승연），韩国女演员。父亲俞昌俊是资深韩国餐厅主厨，母亲在阿姨开的日本餐厅工作。二妹是圈外人。小妹为JYP娱乐旗下女团TWICE成员俞定延，两人2016年7月至隔年1月曾一起为SBS《人气歌谣》担任主持人。此外：她们的亲家表妹是KARD全昭珉。","name":"孔升妍","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"孔升妍","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"孔升妍（朝鮮語：공승연 Gong Seung Yeon，1993 年 2 月 27 日－），本名俞昇延（朝鮮語：유승연），韓國女演員。父親俞昌俊是資深韓國餐廳主廚，母親在阿姨開的日本餐廳工作。二妹是圈外人。小妹為 JYP 娛樂旗下女團 TWICE 成員俞定延，兩人 2016 年 7 月至隔年 1 月曾一起為 SBS《人氣歌謠》擔任主持人。此外：她們的親家表妹是 KARD 全昭珉。","name":"孔升妍","primary":false}}]}}}}